      "reading_order": 5,
      "text": "Oscillatory motion:-\nWhen a body moves to - and - fro\nabout a fixed point it is said to\nbe in oscillatory motion or vibratory\nmotion. The motion of a pendulum\nand a vibrating string are\nexamples for oscillatory motion."
