      "layout_tag": "paragraph",
      "confidence": 0.9444178938865662,
      "reading_order": 4,
      "text": "Circular motion :-\nWhen the motion of an object is around\na fixed point that is outside the\nobject, it is called circular motion.\nThe motion of a stone tied to a\nstring and whirled in a circle, and\nthe motion of the Earth around\nthe sun are examples of circular motion."
